snippet.title: Humble Originals Review - #31 Stumblehill (July 2018)
snippet.description:
Video review for Stumblehill, the thirty-first game created for the Humble Originals program. 

Check out the rest of this channel to find streams and archives of every Humble Original game, plus other Humble Monthly Bundle games, and anything else.

Twitter: @hughcmitchell
Instagram: www.instagram.com/hughcmitchell/

All feedback greatly appreciated.

Video created by Hugh C. Mitchell (hughcmitchell.com)

Thinking of picking up the next Humble Monthly bundle? If you use my referral code, some of that cash will go to helping me make more videos, which I would really appreciate.

I can't put links to websites in my description, so if you'd like to help me out, paste the following code at the end of the link when you're on the Humble monthly page:

....com/monthly?partner=hughcmitchell

NOTE: I am in no way employed or influenced by Humble Bundle or the Humble Original program, I'm just a fan of unique Indie games.
